{"tid":2440104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"DSE歷史科審題委員會疑安插兩教局官員 考評局員工：變壞得非常快","createTime":"2021-03-09T17:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T07:16:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a113c629d55bafa7ddac79c60232a55591bc6509","tid":2440104,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"去年中學文憑試歷史科有關中日戰爭試題遭批鬥，最終教育局宣告「殺題」，更表明今年將安插專家參與審題。《蘋果》收到匿名投訴，指今年文憑試歷史科審題委員會7名非考評局成員中，已最少有2人任職教育局。《蘋果》根據投訴人提供的成員名單，確認其中兩人與教育局一名高級課程發展主任，以及一名項目主任同名。<br />\n<br />\n該匿名投訴人自稱任職考評局，指今年文憑試歷史科審題委員會已有成員名單，並指其中4人來自教育局，形容考評局情況「變壞得非常快，令人黯然神傷」，信中並附上4人名字及職銜。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》翻查政府網站，發現名單有兩人的姓名與一名現任教育局高級課程發展主任，以及一名項目主任相同。另外兩人則分別為一名近年被借調到教育局的相關學科老師，及局方相關學科專責委員會的主要成員。<br />\n<br />\n考評局回覆《蘋果》時，並未否定上述名單真確性，僅指委員的背景各有不同，包括大學教授、具豐富教學經驗的中學教師或校長，亦有課程及學科專家。<br />\n<br />\n考評局續指，2022年文憑試起會落實改善擬卷機制，包括委任教育局課程專家以當然委員的身分參與委員會。考評局又強調，如有人違反保密原則，即屬犯法，有機會判監6個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/6JPIYXX56ZFTHET5TKRSM6K3YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2F6JPIYXX56ZFTHET5TKRSM6K3YA%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=9b412c0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2F6JPIYXX56ZFTHET5TKRSM6K3YA%2F&h=47f52312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/6JPIYXX56ZFTHET5TKRSM6K3YA/</a>"},{"pid":"70d0541df2efad6db6a7c38fa33c808b0a9d00ac","tid":2440104,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af96bdad28b3f1ce82841f713fc447af3bd08394","tid":2440104,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3650a1647a3c016c2d89fa78775d1232da45b663","tid":2440104,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94603d2878a6735670cdba29c9e03c6cec61eb24","tid":2440104,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:58:26.000Z","msg":"唔安插點算愛國，下次安插個黨委書記去你公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007b718677fa11ae5df496b1d0b343e4bbe9a2a6","tid":2440104,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}